		<element kind="staticText" uuid="0890bc87-8ead-4118-9d3e-917cb77fd4cc" x="0" y="21" width="380" height="20" fontSize="7.0">
			<text><![CDATA[we strive to restire your eyewear. Exact replication may not always be possible due to the nature of damage. We are not responsible for pre-existing damage unrelated to the repair.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="23bf6e44-7ea0-4e7b-bf8e-bb7ceba89c25" x="0" y="40" width="380" height="10" fontSize="7.0">
			<text><![CDATA[Additional charges apply for new part; we'll notify you first.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="1ae96c0d-67d4-4e62-b9c9-59adb9fcfa81" x="0" y="50" width="380" height="10" fontSize="7.0">
			<text><![CDATA[Eyeware not picked up within 30 days will incur storage fees or be discarded.]]></text>
		</element>
		<element kind="staticText" uuid="0845f6f9-0693-440c-9e97-3102538e551c" x="0" y="60" width="380" height="10" fontSize="7.0">
			<text><![CDATA[while handled with care, we are not liable for unforeseen damage during repair, especially with delicate or aged frames.]]></text>
		</element>
